Class SlapParamSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • dalserver.ParamSet

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<Param>

    public class SlapParamSet
extends ParamSet
    Construct an initial default parameter set containing the parameters for a SLAP service. Currently this paramset contains the combined parameters for all SLAP operations. A list of the currently defined parameters, including their name, type, and description, can be found in this table.
